More than 40 percent of individual donations made to Northrup, Quinones, and Rosenberg

have been under $100

The majority of individual donations to Lasher’s campaign fall between $100 and $1,000. Quinones has received no donations of greater than $1,000.

Over 96 percent of donations to Quinones have been under $100.
